snippet.title: El Paso, Elsewhere - Old Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
STAKES. GUNS. SLOW-MO. Fight werewolves and vampires in a reality-shifting motel. Dive through barricades to escape the grasp of evil puppets. Destroy the villain you loved. El Paso, Elsewhere is a new, third-person love letter to classic shooters. Neo-noir never looked so good.
